apabilities\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Research and development into new, appropriate, technologies\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Efficient, mobile training solutions - reducing your costs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Exploitation of commercial technologies lowers cost\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Independent of specific tools, technologies and platforms\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Significant domain experience with virtual reality and augmented reality\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3360.00 per unit per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92484/7610418165868517-pricing-document-2015-10-05-1143.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92484/7610418165868517-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-01-1942.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92484/7610418165868517-service-definition-document-2015-10-05-0729.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n  